T10TD4187E:67a-4: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //

T10TD4187E:67b-0: mchog tu brtse ba'i pha ma mdza' bshes @67b gnyen 'dun tshogs //
T10TD4187E:67b-1: mchil ma'i thal ba bzhin du ltos med yal dor nas //
T10TD4187E:67b-2: mtha' 'khob kla klo mun pa'i nang na gcig 'khyams pa //
T10TD4187E:67b-3: blo ldan bu de shes rab sgron mas snang gyur cig / shin tu brtse ba'i ded dpon bdag gis ni //
T10TD4187E:67b-4: legs bshad rgya mtsho'i gling nas blangs pa yi //
T10TD4187E:67b-5: spring yig rin chen 'di ni bu la bskur //
T10TD4187E:67b-6: rab gus dga' zhing dad pas mnyan par gyis //

T10TD4187E:67b-8: g-yo med sems kyis rgyun du brtse ba yi //
T10TD4187E:67b-9: pha ma mdza' bshes rtsa lag spangs nas ni //
T10TD4187E:67b-10: bu khyod mtha' 'khob rgyu ba shin tu smad //
T10TD4187E:67b-11: dam chos phyir ni pha ma yal dor nas //
T10TD4187E:67b-12: nor bzang bzhin du yul gzhan rgyu 'os na //
T10TD4187E:67b-13: 'dod pa'i don du pha ma yal dor nas //
T10TD4187E:67b-14: smad pa'i don du rgyu ba ga la rigs //
T10TD4187E:67b-15: bu khyod gzugs sdug mchog dang sgra snyan dang //
T10TD4187E:67b-16: dri zhim ro mchog reg bya'i bde byed pa //
T10TD4187E:67b-18: dper na glang chen 'dam du chud pa bzhin //
T10TD4187E:67b-19: 'dod pa las ni 'jigs dang sdug bsngal dang //
T10TD4187E:67b-20: mya ngan dang ni 'tshe ba sna tshogs 'byung //
T10TD4187E:67b-21: gsod dang bcing dang yan lag gcod pa dang //

T10TD4187E:67b-23: 'dod la brkam pas sems can dmyal ba dang //
T10TD4187E:67b-24: yi dags dud 'gro rnams su sdug bsngal rnyed //
T10TD4187E:67b-25: mir gyur na yang sdug bsngal mi snyan dang //
T10TD4187E:67b-26: dri mi zhim dang bkres skom mad kyis gzir //
T10TD4187E:67b-27: g-yen ba can la prug na bde //
T10TD4187E:67b-29: de bas 'dod pa med pa bde //
T10TD4187E:67b-30: ji ltar me long brag ca dang //
T10TD4187E:67b-31: spos snod gzar bu nam mkha' rnams //
T10TD4187E:67b-32: gzugs brnyan sgra grags spos dang ni //
T10TD4187E:67b-33: tshod ma'i ro dang rlung rnams kyis //

T10TD4187E:67b-39: nam yang roms par 'gyur ba med //

T10TD4187E:67b-41: 'phags pa'i chos rnams bsten par bya //
T10TD4187E:67b-42: tshul khrims ting 'dzin shes rab mchog / rnam grol bde bas ngoms par 'gyur //
T10TD4187E:67b-43: 'dod la chags pa spang bar bya'o //
T10TD4187E:67b-44: nor la chags pas 'dir gdung phyi mar gdung //
T10TD4187E:68a-0: @68a * // gnyis kar gdung ste des na bdag nyid kyis //
T10TD4187E:68a-1: las rnam smin mthong de gdung rab tu gdung //
T10TD4187E:68a-2: 'gro ba dman par song bas phyir zhing gdung //

T10TD4187E:68a-5: nor la chags pas g-yeng bar gyur pa rnams //
T10TD4187E:68a-6: srid pa'i sdug bsngal las grol skabs med do //
T10TD4187E:68a-7: nor gyi phyir ni rgyal bu dge don gyi //

T10TD4187E:68a-9: bu mo mdza' bo rna ba bye ba ri //
T10TD4187E:68a-10: rgya mtshor shi 'phos 'khyam par gyur pa yin //

T10TD4187E:68a-15: rdzu 'phrul chen po'i rta rgyal ba la has //
T10TD4187E:68a-16: de dag bsgral bar nus pa ma yin no //

T10TD4187E:68a-22: nor gyi phung po la ni dbang bsgyur kyang //

T10TD4187E:68a-29: lus srog yal bar dor nas nor bsags kyang //
T10TD4187E:68a-30: shin skal ba nyams par 'gyur ba yi //
T10TD4187E:68a-31: nor de rmi lam sprin dang mtshungs pa yin //

T10TD4187E:68a-33: nor mang bsags shing sba byas kyang //
T10TD4187E:68a-34: cung zad cung zad sbyad pa yis //

T10TD4187E:68b-35: bud med shin tu mi bzad pa //

T10TD4187E:68b-52: skyes pa bud med ngoms mi 'gyur //

T10TD4187E:68b-55: skyes pa gzhon nu thams cad kyis //
T10TD4187E:69a-2: byi bo byed pa'i ngang tshul can //

T10TD4187E:69a-8: sems can dmyal ba rnams su skye //
T10TD4187E:69a-9: de bas bu khyod de spongs shig / byi bo byed pa shal ma li //
T10TD4187E:69a-10: lcags kyi tsher ma rtse mo 'bar //
T10TD4187E:69a-11: sor ni bcu drug yod pa la //
T10TD4187E:69a-14: mche rno lus che 'bar ba yis //
T10TD4187E:69a-15: gzhan gyi bud med 'phrog pa la //

T10TD4187E:69a-17: gal te chung mar brten na yang //

T10TD4187E:69a-19: drag shul can gyi mdo las gsungs //

T10TD4187E:69a-23: // / gang zhig 'thungs nas ra ro glo nas gom tshugs dbang med 'od ;
T10TD4187E:69a-24: / yul grong ma 'dris par yang 'khyam zhing brdeg 'chos 'gyur //
T10TD4187E:69a-25: bza' dang mi bza' spyad med dug dang 'dres pa za //

T10TD4187E:69a-27: gang 'thungs na ni bdag la brtan med blo nyams shing //
T10TD4187E:69a-28: phyugs dang 'dra bar mdza' bos spong zhing dgra bos 'phya //
T10TD4187E:69a-29: 'dus pa bro gar byed cing glu len 'khar rda rdung //
T10TD4187E:69a-30: dge legs grags nyams rgyu de su zhig 'thung bar byed //
T10TD4187E:69a-31: de 'thungs ngo tsha khrel yod dor nas ni //
T10TD4187E:69a-32: gcer bur byung kyang 'dzem med smyon pa bzhin //
T10TD4187E:69a-33: rkun po gcan gzan rgyu ba'i lam du 'gro //
T10TD4187E:69a-34: lus srog nyams rgyu de ni khyod kyis spangs //
T10TD4187E:69a-35: de 'thungs skyugs pas gos shing 'gyel gyur nas //
T10TD4187E:69a-36: kha yang khyi yis dogs pa med par ldags //
T10TD4187E:69a-37: dran med lam po cher yang nyal gyur na //
T10TD4187E:69a-38: bag med rtsa ba rtag tu spang bar bya //
T10TD4187E:69a-39: gang zhig 'thungs nas myos par 'khrul 'gyur te //
T10TD4187E:69a-40: 'bris na aan dha dag kyang rme byung na //
T10TD4187E:69a-41: du chen 'thib ste phan tshun thal mar byung //
T10TD4187E:69a-42: phung khrol rtsa ba de ni su zhig 'thung //
T10TD4187E:69a-43: gang zhig 'thungs na dpal gyi gzhir 'gyur rigs //
T10TD4187E:69a-44: je mtho je mtho gyur pa'ang rlag byed pa //
T10TD4187E:69a-45: nor gyi dbyig ldan khyim kyang phung 'gyur ba //
T10TD4187E:69a-46: nyes mang gzhi rtsa de ni su zhig 'thung //
T10TD4187E:69a-47: glo bur du zhing re 'ga' dgod par byed //
T10TD4187E:69b-0: @69b ma nges smra zhing gdon gyis zin pa bzhin //
T10TD4187E:69b-1: dam pas smad cing brnyas pa'i gnas gyur pa //
T10TD4187E:69b-2: 'khrul slad rgyu de su zhig 'thung bar byed //
T10TD4187E:69b-3: bag yod rnams kyang de 'thungs sems nyams shing //
T10TD4187E:69b-4: bdag la phan pa'i lam du mi 'jug pa //
T10TD4187E:69b-5: ma brtags mang du smra zhing tshig rtsub 'byin //
T10TD4187E:69b-6: sgo gsum nyams byed de ni btung mi bya //
T10TD4187E:69b-7: gang gi nyes pas sngon gyi lha rnams myos //
T10TD4187E:69b-8: lha yi dbang po'i dpal ni nyams gyur nas //
T10TD4187E:69b-9: skyabs 'dod phyir na rgya mtsho'i nang du gab //

T10TD4187E:69b-15: sdig pa'i srin mo byur ngan mngon sum bzhin //
T10TD4187E:69b-16: rtsod pa'i gzhi dang tha dad ma yin pa //

T10TD4187E:69b-18: de 'thungs yid ni rab tu 'khrugs gyur nas //
T10TD4187E:69b-19: brtse ba'i pha dang ma yang gsod 'gyur zhing //
T10TD4187E:69b-20: nyes med dge sbyong bram ze drang srong gsod //

T10TD4187E:69b-22: rdzun dang phra ma tshig rtsub 'khyal pa smra //
T10TD4187E:69b-23: brnab sems gnod sems log lta'i mun pa 'dzin //

T10TD4187E:69b-26: shes rab lta ba 'tsho ba cho ga dang //
T10TD4187E:69b-27: dran pa shes bzhin dad pa brtson 'grus nyams //
T10TD4187E:69b-28: dge chos chud gzon de ni btung mi bya //
T10TD4187E:69b-29: de 'thungs sdig spyod rnams ni lus zhig nas //
T10TD4187E:69b-30: rab tu bzod dka'i sems can dmyal bar ltung //
T10TD4187E:69b-31: yi dvags dud 'gro rnams kyang smyon par 'gyur //
T10TD4187E:69b-32: sdug bsngal rtsa ba de ni btung mi bya //
T10TD4187E:69b-33: thub pas dga' ba can gyi mdo las ni //
T10TD4187E:69b-34: myos 'gyur nyes pa sum cu rtsa lnga gsungs //
T10TD4187E:69b-35: de phyir bu khyod bdag la phan 'dod na //
T10TD4187E:69b-36: nyes kun rtsa ba de ni btung mi bya //
T10TD4187E:69b-37: chang dga' dgos pa thams cad la //
T10TD4187E:69b-38: rtag tu bag med spyod par 'gyur //
T10TD4187E:69b-39: mkhas pa rnams kyi sman 'gyur zhing //
